        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer423743617" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer504914815348175329">“Fritzy, Fritzy DumbAss!” =)))<br/>Oh my good god, this is one of my most effective sadness treatments, I&apos;ve read it dozens of times, both the original English one and the translated Farsi edition, both of which are hilarious in their own ways. It&apos;s one of those rare books that make me laugh my ass off, out loud, literally. I love it!</span>
  <span id="freeText504914815348175329" style="display:none">“Fritzy, Fritzy DumbAss!” =)))<br />Oh my good god, this is one of my most effective sadness treatments, I've read it dozens of times, both the original English one and the translated Farsi edition, both of which are hilarious in their own ways. It's one of those rare books that make me laugh my ass off, out loud, literally. I love it!</span>
